Me, I made my life.

663
01:05:46,100 --> 01:05:48,700
Perfect young man.

664
01:05:49,100 --> 01:05:51,500
Perfect career.

665
01:05:51,900 --> 01:05:54,800
Perfect fiancee.

666
01:05:57,500 --> 01:06:02,000
