It's very sad.

667
01:06:02,200 --> 01:06:06,000
Where have you been?
I didn't know what to do.

668
01:06:06,300 --> 01:06:08,200
Get a spoon.
-What?

669
01:06:08,600 --> 01:06:10,400
A spoon.

670
01:06:11,800 --> 01:06:14,700
Fill it to thirty.

671
01:06:20,200 --> 01:06:22,100
